WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Five, four, three, two, one, ignition.

2
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:13.000
And this is the LB Minotaur launch vehicle.

3
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:19.000
We're carrying the AA2 launch abort system for a full express test.

4
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:52.000
10 seconds, we will see the abort.

5
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:57.000
Fire is one and two, discharge both sides.

6
00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Pitching for pressure.

7
00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Good control.

8
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:14.000
Rear orientation.

9
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Satellite phase.

10
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:24.000
Fire is three and four, discharge both sides.

11
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Squib power enabled.

